high_descs: Turn right and walk to the front of the fridge then look up at the freezer.
Take a tomato from the freezer then close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the tomato off in the sink then pick it up.
Walk to the trash can between the sink and the fridge.
Put the tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean, cold tomato in the trash can.

high_descs: Move to your right a step then walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and grab the tomato that's on the top shelf and close the door.
Take two steps to your right to face the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Move a tiny bit to your right.
Put the tomato in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn right and go toward the door, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Take a tomato from inside the top of the fridge.
Go to the sink to your left.
Clean the tomato inside of the sink.
Go to the trash bin to your right.
Put the tomato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in the trash.
